import React from 'react';
import Wrapper from './components/Wrapper'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import NavItems from './components/NavItems'
import NavItem from './components/NavItem'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom'
import About from './containers/About'
import Contact from './containers/Contact'
import Home from './containers/Home'

import { Button, SmallContainer } from './components'


class App extends React.Component {
	render() {
	return(
		<Router>
		    	<Navbar top>
		    		<NavItems justify='left'>
		    			<SmallContainer width='60px'><Button> lol </Button></SmallContainer> 					    			
		    		</NavItems>
		    		<NavItems justify='center'>	 
		    			<NavItem ref='b1' onClick={()=>{ console.log('hey') } }><Link to='/'>HOME</Link></NavItem>
			    		<NavItem><Link to='/about'>ABOUT</Link></NavItem>
			    		<NavItem><Link to='/contact'>CONTACT</Link></NavItem>
		    		</NavItems>
		    	</Navbar>
		    	
		    <Wrapper>



		        <Switch>
		          <Route path="/about">
		            <About />
		          </Route>
		          <Route path="/contact">
		            <Contact />
		          </Route>	          
		          <Route path="/">
		            <Home />
		          </Route>
		        </Switch>	    

		    </Wrapper>
		</Router>
	);
	}
}

export default App;
